# üï∑Ô∏è SCRAPER CONFIGURATION
# Cron schedule for automatic data updates (default: daily at 2 AM)
# Format: "minute hour day month weekday"
# Examples:
#   "0 2 * * *"      - Daily at 2 AM
#   "0 */6 * * *"    - Every 6 hours
#   "0 2,14 * * *"   - Twice daily (2 AM and 2 PM)
